title: Pair of Earrings
description: earrings consist of three concentric rings attached by a rectangle at the top; rectangle has 3 spheres on each side and one in the center; curlicue curved ear piece is attached to the rectangle; rings have etchings with yin/yang motif in the center, birds on the left and fish on the right
creditline: The Suzanne S. Roberts Fund for Asian Art
